{"ts":1774974620782,"jobId":"1b826305-b255-4d80-b282-f51494c67425","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"🌙 Goodnight, Nrexya 🤍\n\nHere's a little story before you close your eyes tonight.\n\nIn 1911, a man named Hiram Bingham — a young Yale professor — was hiking through the mountains of Peru, searching for a lost city the locals kept whispering about.\n\nHe followed a small boy who said, \"There are ruins up there.\"\n\nWhat he found was Machu Picchu — an entire Incan city hidden above the clouds, abandoned for 400 years, swallowed by jungle, untouched by the outside world.\n\nStones so perfectly carved that not even a knife blade fits between them. Terraces, temples, fountains — all silent, all waiting.\n\nThe world had forgotten it existed. But the mountains kept it safe.\n\nSometimes the most beautiful things aren't lost. They're just waiting to be found again — by someone brave enough to keep climbing.\n\nSleep well, and trust the climb. 🌿✨","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-delivered","sessionId":"310c0c2a-d646-4f6f-b3e6-d2c0771e2346","sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:1b826305-b255-4d80-b282-f51494c67425:run:310c0c2a-d646-4f6f-b3e6-d2c0771e2346","runAtMs":1774974600015,"durationMs":20761,"nextRunAtMs":1775061000000,"model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","provider":"kilocode","usage":{"input_tokens":16845,"output_tokens":322,"total_tokens":19882}}
